Load phase Seven DF agents are created and some of them register themselves to other DFs such that the resulting graph of DFs has the following arcs:
arc1 = (df5,df6) (read as df5 is registered on df6)
arc2 = (df4,df5)
arc3 = (df2,df4)
arc4 = (df2,df4)
arc5 = (df3,df1)
arc6 = (df1,df2)
arc7 = (df1,df)
After the federation has been created some agents are registered:
df6 = {a14}
df5 = {a13}
df4 = {a11,a12}
df2 = {a2,a3,a4}
df3 = {a5,a6,a7,a8,a9,a10}
df1 = {a1}
df ={}
where each agent offers different services (use DF gui to have more details).
